Easy Backup
Easy Troubleshooting

Search:

kubectl get pods -l criticality=high
Expert Scenario 2
Prometheus Monitoring

Monitor only production applications.

Query:

env=prod

Prometheus discovers applications using labels.

Used heavily in enterprises.

Expert Scenario 3
Backup Strategy

Backup only critical applications.

Labels:

backup: required

Find:

kubectl get pods -l backup=required

Automation becomes simple.

Production Label Standard

Most enterprises follow:

labels:
  app: payment-api
  env: prod
  team: devops
  version: v1
  backup: required

Example:

labels:
  app: sap-fiori
  env: prod
  owner: basis-team
  version: v2
Troubleshooting Labs
Scenario 1

Service not routing traffic.

Check:

kubectl describe svc

Verify:

kubectl get endpoints

Look for:

Label mismatch
Scenario 2

Deployment not creating Pods.

Check:

kubectl describe deployment

Possible cause:

Selector mismatch
Scenario 3

ReplicaSet not managing Pod.

Verify:

kubectl get pods --show-labels

Check selector.

Scenario 4

Find all production applications.

kubectl get pods -l env=prod
